HEADWORD: Pyruvic
<hw>Py*ru"vic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Pyro-</ets> +
L. <ets>uva</ets> a grape.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to,
